<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Sentrachem says considering Dow offer.</title>
<headline>Sentrachem says considering Dow offer.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-08-05</dateline>
<text>
<p>Chemical group Sentrachem Ltd said on Tuesday it was considering its response to an offer by The Dow Chemical Co to buy the company for 10.50 rand a share.</p>
<p>It said a further announcement would be made shortly, but until then, shareholders were advised to exercise caution in their dealing in Sentrachem shares.</p>
<p>Its shares were last trading at 10.00 rand each -- a 208 cent gain from Monday.</p>
